title: Why each Libra member’s mutiny hurts Facebook
text: There’s a strategic cost to the defection of Visa, Stripe, eBay, and more from the Facebook -led cryptocurrency Libra Association . They’re not just names dropping off a list.

title: Warren runs a false Facebook ad to protest false Facebook ads
text: Presidential candidate Elizabeth Warren isn't happy about Facebook's policy that exempts politicians' posts from fact-checking.

title: Warren Dares Facebook With Intentionally False Political Ad
text: The Democratic presidential candidate bought the ad to goad Facebook into removing misinformation in political ads, escalating her feud with the social network.

title: Warren trolls Facebook election ad policy with a 'false' ad that says company endorsed Trump
text: While Warren's ad about Facebook isn't true, the company's own policy allows politicians to make such false claims in paid advertising.
